extends layouts/default.pug

block prepend head
    - var pageTitle = "KİLER İPLİK - OPEN-END YARN PRODUCTION "
    - var pageDescription = "OPEN-END YARN PRODUCTION "
    - var pageName = "Home"
    - var pageClass = "page-body-class"

block content
  div(class='aspect-square lg:aspect-1920/560 relative -z-10')
    img(src=dirAssets + 'banner.jpg' alt='anasayfa' class='w-full h-full object-cover')
    div(class='banner-title') 
      h1 
        | OPEN-END YARN PRODUCTION 

  section(class='container max-w-screen-md py-12')
    p(class='text-center') 
      | In open-end yarn production, we operate a fully automated system at every stage, from production to packaging. Equipped with cutting-edge machinery, our facility prioritizes high-quality yarn production. This advanced system ensures maximum precision in production processes while significantly enhancing efficiency.

  section(class='section-bg before:top-0 py-6 mb-12')
    div(class='container text-center')
      h2(class='text-lg py-4 lg:py-6 lg:text-xl')
        | OPEN-END YARN PRODUCTION IMAGES
    div(class='container mb-8 lg:mb-12 lg:max-w-screen-lg')
      div(class='swiper swiper-trigger !pb-12')
        div(class='swiper-wrapper')
          div(class='swiper-slide')
            div(class='aspect-gallery rounded-3xl lg:rounded-[80px] overflow-hidden')
              img(src=dirAssets + 'slide-3.jpg' alt='slide-3' class='w-full h-full object-cover')
          div(class='swiper-slide')
            div(class='aspect-gallery rounded-3xl lg:rounded-[80px] overflow-hidden')
              img(src=dirAssets + 'slide-2.jpg' alt='slide-2' class='w-full h-full object-cover')
          div(class='swiper-slide')
            div(class='aspect-gallery rounded-3xl lg:rounded-[80px] overflow-hidden')
              img(src=dirAssets + 'slide-1.jpg' alt='slide-1' class='w-full h-full object-cover')
        div(class='swiper-pagination')
        div(class='swiper-button-prev')
        div(class='swiper-button-next')

